---
source: src/setup/mod.rs
expression: "plan(Profile::Dev)"
---
hpds setup --profile dev runs these 7 steps:
  1. r
       hpds install r
  2. quarto
       hpds install quarto
  3. uv
       hpds install uv
  4. gh
       hpds install gh
  5. rig
       hpds install rig
  6. tinytex
       hpds install tinytex
  7. git setup
       hpds git setup
